Sliders Flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Gadget:	<Sliders=>sliders>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0	- If set then deliver value changes as user clicks/drags.
	1	- If set then deliver value changes constantly, otherwise just at start/end.
	3	- If set then slider is vertical.
	4	- If set slider is clickable/draggable.
	12-15 	- Desktop colour of the bar.
	12-15 	- Desktop colour of the background.

Constants:
	<Slider_GenerateValueChangedEndOfDrag>
	<Slider_GenerateValueChangedDuringDrag>
	<Slider_GenerateSetValueChanged>
	<Slider_Vertical>
	<Slider_Draggable>
	<Slider_BarColour>
	<Slider_BarColourShift>
	<Slider_BackgroundColour>
	<Slider_BackgroundColourShift>
	<Slider_ValueChanged_EndOfDrag>
	<Slider_ValueChanged_DuringDrag>
	<Slider_LowerBound>
	<Slider_UpperBound>
	<Slider_StepSize>
To be used with <Gadget_Set_Flags=>Gadget_Set_Flags>
